                                </p>
                                            <p style="padding-left: 50px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -42px; padding-bottom:2px; line-height:27px; margin-top:-10px;"> <span style="padding-left: 30px;white-space: nowrap;">(a)</span> <span style="padding-left:10px; ">Healthy and eco-friendly water treatment for the <span style="padding-left:35px;">pool.</span></span></p>
                                            <p style="padding-left: 50px;line-height:5px; text-indent: -42px; text-align: justify;"><span style="padding-left: 30px;white-space: nowrap;"> (b)</span><span style="padding-left:12px;"> Improved quality of pool water.</span></p>
