                                            <p style="padding-left: 50px; text-indent: -42px;line-height:12px; text-align: justify;"> <span style="padding-left: 30px;white-space: nowrap;">(d)</span><span style="padding-left:12px;"> Reduced chances of sensitizing allergies.</span></p>
                                            <p style="padding-left: 50px; text-indent: -42px;line-height:12px; text-align: justify;"> <span style="padding-left: 30px;white-space: nowrap;">(e)</span> <span style="padding-left:15px;">No smell of chlorine.</span></p>
                                            <p style="padding-left: 50px; text-indent: -42px;line-height:12px; text-align: justify;"> <span style="padding-left: 30px;white-space: nowrap;">(f)</span> <span style="padding-left:18px;">Non-toxic, hence, no side effects.</span></p>

                                        </td>
